---
import { SHOP_URL, SHOP_LABEL, LINE_ID, LINE_URL } from "../config";
---

<aside class="grid-promo" aria-label="選購與諮詢提示">
  <p class="grid-promo__eyebrow">讀完想下單？</p>
  <p class="grid-promo__text">
    本站為選購參考，現貨與規格請至<strong>{SHOP_LABEL}</strong>確認；也可加 LINE 詢問口味與售後。
  </p>
  <a class="grid-promo__shop" href={SHOP_URL} rel="noopener noreferrer">前往{SHOP_LABEL}</a>
  <a class="grid-promo__line" href={LINE_URL} rel="noopener noreferrer">
    LINE ID：{LINE_ID}
  </a>
</aside>
